    "These challenges hinder the models from effectively learning differentiating features.",
    "Despite showcasing commendable performance on demanding datasets, the framework is not immune to limitations.",
    "From the results of our experiments, it is apparent that the network encounters challenges in distinguishing between two closely resembling images representing different classes.",
    "The inter-class similarity across various categories prompts the network to learn features that are too similar, leading to misclassifications within the framework.Similarly, RSSCN7 presents unique challenges due to its higher inter-class similarity, varied backgrounds, and complex scene compositions, especially across natural landscapes.",
    "This dataset includes categories with overlapping visual characteristics, making it more challenging for the RCA network to differentiate between classes."
